Reported deaths in Africa reached 238 655 and 9 674 632 people have recovered. South Africa has the most reported cases   3 603 856 and 95,022 people died. 

Other most-affected countries are Morocco (1 131 395), Tunisia (901 107), Ethiopia ( 464 930 ), Libya (434 095 ), Egypt (423 688)  and Kenya (321 335). --Allafrica--